data.description: ORIGINAL PRICE REDUCED ABOUT $10K!  Home looks like new with recent remodeling and updates: A/C unit, commodes, dining chandelier, secondary bathtub with sliding glass door and garage door opener with remote, all replaced in 2021/2022. Additionally, kitchen remodeled in August 2022 with new vinyl plank flooring, new stainless steel 5-burner gas stove with vented hood, new stainless steel double sink, granite countertop with beautiful backsplash, and cabinets repainted. Great and quiet neighborhood off Beltway 8 South and Hilcroft Street with quick access and proximity to Hwy 90, Hwy 288 & I-59. Wow! No mandatory annual dues. Low Tax Rate of 2.1. Come see it!
